# A2R Webhook Ingestion Service

## Environment Variables

```bash
# Server Configuration
WEBHOOK_PORT=8787
WEBHOOK_HOST=0.0.0.0
WEBHOOK_LOG_LEVEL=info

# CORS Configuration
WEBHOOK_CORS_ORIGINS=*

# Webhook Secrets (HMAC verification)
WEBHOOK_GITHUB_SECRET=gh_secret_123
WEBHOOK_DISCORD_SECRET=dc_secret_456
WEBHOOK_ANTFARM_SECRET=af_secret_789
WEBHOOK_MOLTBOOK_SECRET=mb_secret_012

# Rails Integration
A2R_RAILS_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3011
A2R_RAILS_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=60
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000

# Idempotency / Deduplication
DEDUP_TTL_SECONDS=3600
DEDUP_CLEANUP_INTERVAL_SECONDS=300
```

## Usage

```bash
# Start webhook server
pnpm serve

# Or with options
pnpm serve --port 8787 --log-level debug

# List configured webhooks
pnpm list

# Trigger test webhook
pnpm trigger --source github --event pull_request.opened
```

## Webhook Endpoints

### POST /webhook/:source

Receive webhooks from a specific source.

```bash
# GitHub webhook
curl -X POST http://localhost:8787/webhook/github \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "X-Hub-Signature-256: sha256=abc123..." \
  -d @github-payload.json

# Discord webhook
curl -X POST http://localhost:8787/webhook/discord \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d @discord-payload.json
```

### POST /webhook

Generic webhook endpoint (source in body).

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8787/webhook \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"source": "custom", "eventType": "my.event", "customData": {...}}'
```

### GET /health

Health check endpoint.

```bash
curl http://localhost:8787/health
```

Response:
```json
{
  "status": "healthy",
  "timestamp": "2026-03-08T12:00:00.000Z",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "stats": {
    "deduplication": {
      "total": 42,
      "byStatus": { "processed": 40, "pending": 2 },
      "bySource": { "github": 30, "discord": 12 }
    }
  }
}
```

## Supported Sources

| Source    | Event Types                          | Signature |
|-----------|--------------------------------------|-----------|
| GitHub    | pull_request.*, issues.*, push, etc. | HMAC-SHA256 |
| Discord   | message.*, member.*, reaction.*      | Optional  |
| Ant Farm  | room.*, task.*                       | Optional  |
| Moltbook  | post.*, comment.*, mention.*         | Optional  |
| Custom    | Any                                  | Optional  |

## Architecture

```
┌─────────────────┐
│  External       │
│  Services       │
│  (GitHub, etc.) │
└────────┬────────┘
         │ Webhook POST
         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Webhook Server (Fastify)               │
│  - Rate Limiting                        │
│  - Signature Verification               │
│  - Allowlist Validation                 │
└────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
         │ Normalized Event
         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Normalizer Registry                    │
│  - GitHub Normalizer                    │
│  - Discord Normalizer                   │
│  - Ant Farm Normalizer                  │
│  - Moltbook Normalizer                  │
└────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
         │ Canonical Event
         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Idempotency Check                      │
│  - Deduplication Store                  │
│  - Idempotency Key Generation           │
└────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
         │ Unique Event
         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Rails Event Emitter                    │
│  - ExternalEventReceived                │
│  - WorkRequestCreated (if needed)       │
│  - AgentMentioned (if @mentioned)       │
└────────┬────────────────────────────────┘
         │ Receipts
         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Receipt Recorder                       │
│  - Immutable Evidence                   │
│  - Audit Trail                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

